%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20ceding%20the%20stage%2C%20they%20went%20digital.%20They%20launched%20their%20own%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20and%20their%20supporters%20spearheaded%20online%20and%20offline%20campaigns%20and%20created%20alternative%20news%20channels.%20This%20counteroffensive%20transformed%20the%20fight%20into%20a%20three-pronged%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20became%20more%20than%20just%20a%20contest%20between%20the%20establishment%20and%20the%20anti-establishment.%20It%20morphed%20into%20a%20clash%20between%20traditional%20media%20and%20the%20burgeoning%20power%20of%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%E2%80%99s%20digital%20insurgency%20challenged%20the%20long-held%20dominance%20of%20traditional%20media%20and%20carved%20out%20a%20space%20for%20their%20voices%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%20may%20be%20set%2C%20the%20digital%20battleground%20shows%20a%20new%20force%20has%20emerged%20in%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20future%20of%20the%20cross-strait%20relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20international%20front%2C%20continuity%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20watchword.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20established%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%2C%20nurtured%20by%20President%20Tsai%20Ing-wen%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Vice%20President%20Bi%20khim%20Hsiao.%20Her%20esteemed%20record%20as%20former%20ambassador%20to%20the%20US%20inspires%20confidence%20in%20maintaining%20strong%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20cross-strait%20relations%20with%20China%20face%20a%20potential%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20President%20and%20Vice%20President%20openly%20supporting%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20independence%20in%20the%20past%2C%20China%20perceives%20them%20as%20a%20united%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fpage%2F202311%2F1302696.shtml%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cindependence%20duo%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20stance%20may%20trigger%20harsh%20responses%2C%20from%20further%20curtailing%20trade%20via%20terminating%20the%20free%20trade%20agreement%20to%20heightened%20military%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20forward%20requires%20navigating%20a%20delicate%20balance%20of%20upholding%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20values%20while%20recognising%20the%20complex%20geopolitical%20realities.%20The%20future%20of%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20cross-strait%20relationship%20hinges%20on%20how%20well%20this%20balance%20is%20upheld.%20The%20governing%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20will%20be%20judged%20on%20how%20they%20walk%20the%20tightrope.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taiwan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%E2%80%99s%20emergence%20may%20seem%20to%20add%20another%20layer%20of%20complexity%2C%20with%20its%20potentially%20divergent%20views%20on%20cross-strait%20policy.%20The%20party%20believes%20demonstrating%20goodwill%20can%20lower%20the%20temperature%20and%20avoid%20harsher%20measures%20like%20trade%20restrictions%20or%20military%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20unlike%20the%20Kuomintang%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2Fmagazine%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Fcould-taiwan-be-the-next-ukraine-00135009%5C%22%3Eappeasement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Taiwan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20advocates%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpp.org.tw%2Fen%2Four_platform-detail.php%3Fid%3D20%5C%22%3Estrengthening%20national%20defence%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20deter%20aggression%20and%20ensure%20peaceful%20coexistence%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20while%20the%20immediate%20outlook%20for%20cross-strait%20relations%20may%20be%20turbulent%2C%20the%20robust%20growth%20of%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20offers%20a%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20for%20a%20future%20where%20pragmatism%20holds%20sway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaiwan%E2%80%99s%20election%20has%20presented%20a%20paradox%3A%20a%20