short%20video%20of%20the%20commander%20saying%20these%20words%20is%20available%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fshorts%2FC9ijaLFXxbQ%3Fsi%3DIFNVKhK5GKzFH9QB%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20Gen.%20Katiyar%20said%20that%20women%20soldiers%20will%20play%20a%20very%20important%20role%20in%20any%20future%20war.%20%E2%80%9CA%20blueprint%20is%20being%20prepared%20for%20the%20recruitment%20of%20women%20soldiers%20in%20the%20army%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fstrength-of-indian-army-lies-in-its-apolitical-character-western-command-chief-2847937%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reports%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Western%20Command%20of%20army%20noted%20significant%20acts%20of%20valour%20by%20Indian%20army%20personnel%20in%20the%20past%20as%20important%20to%20seek%20inspiration%20from.%20He%20noted%20that%20in%20warfare%20in%20the%20future%2C%20for%20all%20the%20talk%20of%20advancements%20in%20technology%2C%20the%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20role%20will%20remain%20crucial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20positions%2C%20all%20ranks%20also%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20professional%20development%20and%20physical%20fitness%20because%20the%20next%20battle%20will%20be%20high-tech%2C%20and%20it%20will%20also%20be%20in%20difficult%20terrain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20He%20spoke%20of%20the%20significance%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Enaam%2C%20namak%2C%20nishan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20name%2C%20salt%2C%20symbol%20%E2%80%93%20as%20values%20central%20to%20what%20soldiers%20stand%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20Gen%20Katiyar%20took%20over%20this%20present%20post%20in%20July%2C%202023.%20Before%20this%2C%20he%20was%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Military%20operations%20(DGMO)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20General%20Katiyar%20was%20conferred%20with%20the%20Ati%20Vishisht%20Seva%20Medal%20for%20distinguished%20service%20in%202021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EArmy%20Day%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%2076th%20Army%20Day.%20January%2015%20is%20observed%20as%20Army%20Day%2C%20each%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20commemorates%20the%20day%20India%E2%80%99s%20Army%20was%20detangled%20from%20the%20British.%20On%2015%20January%201949%2C%20Field%20Marshal%20K.M.%20Cariappa%20became%20the%20first%20Commander-in-chief%20after%20taking%20over%20from%20the%20British%20Commander-in-Chief%20General%20Francis%20Butcher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20Parade%20is%20held%20at%20the%20Cariappa%20Parade%20Ground%20of%20Delhi%20Cantonment.%C2%A0But%20this%20year%2C%20it%20will%20be%20held%20at%20Lucknow.%20Gen%20Manoj%20Pandey%2C%20Indian%20Army%20Chief%20will%20take%20the%20salute.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20been%20termed%20the%20Shaurya%20Sandhya%20event%2C%20and%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20will%20be%20present.%20The%20theme%20of%20Army%20Day%202024%20is%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIn%20Service%20of%20the%20Nation%E2%80%9D.%20The%20motto%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20is%2C%20%E2%80%9CService%20Before%20Self.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705297423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F15111236%2FUntitled-design-15.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanoj-kumar-katiyar-secular-army-day-apolitical%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lt%20Gen%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Katiyar%2C%20while%20addressing%20soldiers%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20outlined%20core%20strengths%20and%20principles%20without%20which%20he%20said%2C%20the%20army%20would%20be%20harmed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fman