%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%3F%20The%20presence%20of%20a%20'secular'%20government%20does%20not%20imply%20the%20obliteration%20of%20tradition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20hue%20and%20cry%20in%20the%20opposition%20over%20the%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20reportedlys%20skipping%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20decided%20against%20attending%20the%20January%2022%20event%20after%20objecting%20to%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20ceremony%20at%20an%20'incomplete%20temple'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20down%20the%20invite%20for%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20event%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20even%20our%20Shankaracharyas%20(religious%20guru)%20will%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20event%20which%20shows%20that%20the%20reason%20for%20not%20attending%20it%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20politicised%20the%20event%20and%20took%20decisions%2C%20our%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20who%20are%20at%20the%20top%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20and%20guide%20us%2C%20said%20that%20they%20will%20not%20be%20attending%20the%20event.%20This%20has%20become%20such%20an%20issue%20that%20all%20Shankarachariyas%20are%20saying%20they%20will%20boycott%20this%20event.%20If%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20are%20saying%20so%2C%20it%20has%20its%20own%20importance%2C%26quot%3B%20Gehlot%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20minister%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20alleged%20that%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20separate%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20country's%20population%20from%20Lord%20Ram%20by%20putting%20a%20political%20tag%20on%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20of%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20system%20and%20set%20of%20rituals%20to%20perform%20Pran%20Pratishtha.%20If%20this%20event%20is%20religious%2C%20then%20is%20it%20happening%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20of%20the%20four%20Peeths%3F%20All%20four%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20said%20clearly%20that%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20of%20an%20incomplete%20temple%20cannot%20be%20done.%20If%20this%20event%20is%20not%20religious%2C%20then%20it%20is%20political%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreparations%20are%20in%20full%20swing%20for%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20anticipated%20to%20attract%20dignitaries%20and%20individuals%20from%20various%20backgrounds.%20The%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20has%20set%20noon%20on%20January%2022%20as%20the%20moment%20to%20install%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20The%20Vedic%20rituals%20for%20the%20Pran-Pratishtha%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya%20are%20scheduled%20to%20commence%20on%20January%2016%2C%20one%20week%20prior%20to%20the%20main%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705293600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fqu578uu_puri-shankaracharya_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-4-shankaracharyas-are-likely-to-skip-ram-temple-event-not-about-ego-4864921%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Swami%20Nischalanand%20Saraswati%20Maharaj%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20of%20Puri%2C%20disclosed%20that%20their%20decision%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20deviation%20from%20established%20traditions%20during%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-4-shankaracharyas-are-likely-to-skip-ram-temple-event-not-about-ego-4864921%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amp