20before%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%201904%20and%201908%2C%20German%20colonisers%20killed%20more%20than%2070%2C000%20members%20of%20the%20Herero%20and%20Nama%20tribes%2C%20following%20a%20rebellion%20against%20seizure%20of%20land%20and%20cattle.%20As%20per%20the%20UN%2C%20more%20than%2080%20percent%20of%20the%20Herero%20people%20and%20half%20of%20the%20total%20Nama%20population%20were%20killed.%20Historians%20believe%20that%20this%20was%2020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20century%E2%80%99s%20first%20genocide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20German%20statement%20on%20Friday%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20case%20by%20South%20Africa%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20instrumentalization%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20UN%20Genocide%20Convention.%20It%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20view%20of%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20history%20and%20the%20crime%20against%20humanity%20of%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20the%20Government%20sees%20itself%20as%20particularly%20committed%20to%20the%20Convention%20against%20Genocide%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENamibia%20rejects%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20Support%20of%20the%20Genocidal%20Intent%20of%20the%20Racist%20Israeli%20State%20against%20Innocent%20Civilians%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Namibian%20soil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGermany%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Germany%3C%2Fa%3E%20committed%20the%20first%20genocide%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20in%201904-1908%2C%20in%20which%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20innocent%20Namibians%20died%20in%20the%20most%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FZxwWxLv8yt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FZxwWxLv8yt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Namibian%20Presidency%20(%40NamPresidency)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwi