%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106851317.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESevere%20Arctic%20storm%20leaves%20four%20dead%2C%20causes%20widespread%20power%20outages%2C%20and%20disrupts%20daily%20life%20across%20the%20United%20States.%20An%20estimated%2095%20million%20Americans%20are%20under%20weather%20advisories%20due%20to%20dangerously%20low%20wind%20chills.%20Power%20outages%20affect%20tens%20of%20thousands%20in%20multiple%20states.%20Meteorologists%20warn%20of%20near-blizzard%20conditions%20and%20significant%20air%20travel%20disruptions.%20The%20Arctic%20storm%20was%20expected%20to%20bring%204%20to%206%20inches%20of%20snow%20to%20parts%20of%20Arkansas%2C%20northern%20Mississippi%2C%20and%20west%20Tennessee.%20Air%20travel%20was%20severely%20affected%2C%20with%20significant%20cancellations%20and%20delays%20at%20airports%20including%20Buffalo%20Niagara%20International%2C%20Chicago%2C%20Denver%2C%20and%20Seattle-Tacoma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Farctic-blast-brings-below-zero-temperatures-and-disrupts-life-across-the-us%2Farticleshow%2F106851317.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Farctic-blast-brings-below-zero-temperatures-and-disrupts-life-across-the-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F106851317.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Farctic-blast-brings-below-zero-temperatures-and-disrupts-life-across-the-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F106851317.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Jaiswal%2C%20Dube%20Justify%20Team%20India%20Selection%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20Says...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20bag%2C%20India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20on%20Sunday%20said%20he%20is%20happy%20that%20the%20players%20are%20actually%20walking%20the%20talk%20as%20the%20team%20ticks%20all%20the%20boxes%20ahead%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20India%20beat%20Afghanistan%20by%20six%20wickets%20in%20the%20second%20T20I%20to%20take%20an%20unassailable%202-0%20lead%20in%20the%20three-game%20series%2C%20which%20is%20the%20last%20before%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20West%20Indies.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20clear%20with%20what%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20very%20clear%20message%20to%20everyone%20and%20when%20you%20see%20a%20performance%20like%20that%2C%20you%20can%20be%20really%20proud%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20during%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20is%20talking%20about%20it%2C%20but%20to%20actually%20go%20there%20and%20play%20that%20way%20is%20a%20proud%20feeling.%20The%20last%20two%20games%2C%20we've%20ticked%20a%20lot%20of%20boxes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(68)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(63)%20smashed%20brutal%20fifties%20to%20chase%20down%20a%20target%20of%20173%20with%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20had%20a%20great%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20Jaiswal%20has%20played%20Test%20cricket%20now%20and%20even%20T20I.%20He%20has%20shown%20what%20he%20is%20capable%20of.%20He%20has%20the%20talent%20and%20has%20a%20great%20range%20of%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDube%20is%20a%20big%20guy%2C%20very%20powerful%20and%20can%20take%20on%20the%20spinners.%20That%20is%20his%20role%20and%20he%20has%20come%20out%20and%20played%20two%20crucial%20innings%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20match%2C%20Rohit%20also%20became%20the%20first%20male%20cricketer%20in%20history%20to%20play%20150%20T20I%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20great%20feeling%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20long%20journey%20starting%20way%20back%20in%202007.%20I've%20cherished%20every%20moment%20I%20have%20spent%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxar%20Patel%2C%20who%20was%20adjudged%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20for%20his%20two%20wickets%20for%2017%20in%20four%20overs%2C%20said%20he%20tried%20to%20vary%20his%20length%20and%20bowled%20a%20bit%20slower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFeels%20good%2C%20I%20just%20realised%20that%20I%20have%20got%20200%20T20%20wickets.%20But%20what%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20doing%20well%20for%20India%2C%20honestly%20a%20few%20years%20later%20I%20won't%20remember%20how%20many%20wickets%20I%20took%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20bowl%20a%20bit%20slower%2C%20vary%20my%20lengths%20and%20now%20I%20have%20been%20to%20gauge%20these%20things%20better.%20Now%20I%20have%20the%20confidence%20to%20bowl%20at%20all%20times%2C%20even%20in%20the%20powerplay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20be%20mentally%20prepared%20as%20a%20bowler%20in%20T20%20cricket.%20Ready%20to%20concede%20a%20six%20because%20that%20same%20ball%20could%20get%20you%20a%20wicket%20on%20another%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20vary%20my%20plans%20if%20a%20batter%20was%20hitting%20me%2C%20but%20now%20I%20stick%20to%20my%20plans%20and%20make%20the%20batters%20take%20the%20chance%20against%20me.%26quot%3B%20Afghanistan%20skipper%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20said%20they%20have%20been%20playing%20well%20in%20patches%20and%20need%20to%20play%20consistent%20cricket%20throughout%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20quite%20short.%20We%20had%20a%20good%20start%20but%20not%20very%20good%20after%20that.%20Sometimes%20we%20play%20well%20in%20the%20powerplay%2C%20sometimes%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20sometimes%20at%20the%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20build%20the%20momentum%20throughout%20and%20not%20repeat%20mistakes%20to%20have%20a%20good%20T20%20World%20Cup.%26quot%3B%20India%20will%20play%20Afghanistan%20in%20the%20third%20and%20final%20T20I%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20Bengaluru.%20PTI%20ATK%20A