ecration%20of%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%20exactly%20in%20the%20same%20site%20where%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%2C%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20was%20demolished%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20that%20to%20be%20an%20egregious%20violation%20of%20rule%20law.%20There%20is%20massive%20controversy%20being%20generated%20by%20BJP%20around%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20others%20who%20declined%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20much%20hyped-consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20Shankaracharya%20also%20declined%20to%20participate%20on%20several%20grounds%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20not%20completely%20constructed%20and%20so%20it%20is%20in%20contravention%20of%20scriptural%20injunction%20not%20to%20consecrate%20the%20deity%20in%20an%20incomplete%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20visit%20Odisha%20temples%20after%20his%20return%20to%20India%20following%20his%20triumphant%20visit%20to%20the%20USA%20in%201893%20to%20address%20several%20lectures%20including%20in%20the%20famous%20event%20organised%20by%20World%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20here%20is%20an%20example%20of%20cerebral%20monk%20of%20Hinduism%20who%20mesmerised%20Americans%20by%20his%20brilliant%20exposition%20of%20spirituality%20and%20Vedanta%20and%20yet%20was%20told%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20entry%20to%20temples%20of%20Odisha.%20In%20Volume%205%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EComplete%20Works%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20page%20number%20171%2C%20there%20is%20a%20letter%20Swami%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20wrote%20to%20one%20Josephine%20MacLeod.%20In%20that%2C%20he%20wrote%20with%20anguish%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20possible%20to%20see%20the%20Orissan%20temples%20in%20company%20with%20your%20Japanese%20friends%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20know%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20I%20shall%20be%20allowed%20myself%20owing%20to%20my%20eating%20%E2%80%9CMlechchha%20Food%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20dubbed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Emlechchha%3C%2Fem%3E%20food%E2%80%9D%20eater%20because%20he%20ate%20food%20cooked%20by%20Christians%20in%20America%20and%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20those%20temples%20of%20Orissa%2C%20present%20day%20Odisha%2C%20now%20Congress%20leaders%20refusing%20to%20join%20the%20Ram%20temple%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%20are%20dubbed%20as%20Ram-%3Cem%3Edrohis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20traitors%20to%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20illuminating%20to%20not%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20also%20reflected%20on%20the%20establishment%20of%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20which%20was%20established%20in%201885%20by%20Allan%20Octavian%20Hume%2C%20a%20British%20national.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEleven%20years%20later%20in%201896%20while%20Vivekananda%20was%20in%20London%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20a%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CHave%20you%20given%20any%20attention%20to%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20moment%3F%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20response%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20pay%20enough%20attention%20to%20it%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6I%20regard%20the%20movement%20as%20significant%2C%20and%20heartily%20wish%20it%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20he%20said%20that%20a%20nation%20was%20being%20made%20out%20of%20different%20races%20which%20in%20terms%20of%20variety%20remained%20no%20less%20plural%20than%20different%20peoples%20of%20Europe.%20He%20interpreted%20the%20acquisition%20of%20Indian%20trade%20by%20several%20European%20countries%20such%20as%20Britain%2C%20Dutch%2C%20Portugal%20and%20French%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20history%20of%20humanity%E2%80%9D%20and%20described%20that%20the%20trade%20and%20commerce%20of%20India%20played%20%C2%A0a%20%C2%A0tremendous%20part%20in%20the%20civilisation%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20in%20what%20direction%20it%20would%20proceed%20to%20attain%20finality%2C%20Vivekananda%20very%20presciently%2C%20said%20that%20it%20would%20lead%20to%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20working%20out%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20homogeneity%2C%20in%20her%20acquiring%20what%20we%20may%20call%20democratic%20ideas.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%20to%20state%20that%20monopoly%20over%20intelligence%20and%20education%20by%20a%20cultured%20few%20should%20come%20to%20an%20end%2C%20provision%20of%20education%20should%20be%20accompanied%20with%20compulsory%20education%20and%20immense%20power%20of%20people%20should%20be%20utilised%20to%20actualise%20India%E2%80%99s%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vivekananda%20was%20asked%20if%20India%20was%20sensitive%20and%20conscious%20of%20%C2%A0the%20awakening%20that%20he%20alluded%20to%2C%20his%20response%20was%3A%20%E2%80%9CPerfectly%20conscious%2C%20The%20world%20perhaps%20sees%20it%20chiefly%20in%20the%20Congress%20movement%20and%20in%20the%20field%20of%20social%20reform.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201898%20when%20someone%20told%20Swami%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20%C2%A0that%20India%20National%20Congress%20and%20other%20patriotic%20organisations%20were%20carrying%20on%20strenuous%20agitation%20and%20petitioning%20the%20British%20government%2C%20he%20remarked%20that%20the%20rulers%E2%80%99%20duty%20was%20to%20address%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20people.%20In%20that%20context%20he%20flagged%20the%20point%20as%20to%20who%20would%20continue%20to%20place%20people%E2%80%99s%20%C2%A0issues%20before%20the%20government.%20He%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20are%20the%20men%20who%20are%20the%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20things%20demanded%3F%E2%80%9D%20and%20suggested%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20make%20men%20first%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20it%20was%20that%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20spoke%20thus%20of%20just%2013%20years%20after%20the%20establishment%20of%20Congress%20in%201885.%20This%20organisation%20is%20now%20criticised%20by%20none%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fafternoon-brief-congress-founded-by-foreigner-pm-modis-jibe-and-all-the-latest-news-101690268315900.html%5C%22%3Ethan%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20having%20been%20set%20up%20by%20a%20foreigner.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVivekananda%E2%80%99s%20ideas%20in%20the%20context%20of%20agitations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20words%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20are%20the%20men%20who%20are%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20things%20demanded%E2%80%9D%20resonate%20in%20the%20several%20movements%20of%20people%20including%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20now%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20being%20launched%20on%20January%2014.%20His%20vision%20is%20being%20%C2%A0carried%20%C2%A0forward%20by%20people%20engaged%20in%20several%20agitations%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckeep%20up%20things%20demanded.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20why%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20was%20often%20invoking%20the%20stirring%20words%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EUpanishad%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CArise%2C%20awake%20and%20stop%20not%20till%20the%20goal%20is%20reached%E2%80%9D.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20as%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20had%20started%20celebrating%20Swami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20as%20National%20Youth%20Day.%20Days%20after%20his%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20India%20must%20remain%20tuned%20to%20his%20words%20uttered%20in%20Chicago%20%E2%80%93%20that%20%E2%80%9Csectarianism%2C%20bigotry%20and%20its%20horrible%20descendent%20fanaticism%20drenched%20the%20earth%20with%20the%20blood%20of%20innocents%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20hope%20that%20the%20bell%20that%20tolled%20to%20announce%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20World%20Parliament%20of%20Religions%20would%20be%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20fanaticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0S.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Naraya