t%3B%20Trump%20that%20the%20former%20US%20President%20called%20his%20campaign%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20CNN%2C%20Ramaswamy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20interpret%20it%20as%20bad%20campaign%20strategist%20corporate%20consultant%20advice%20that%20he%20might%20have%20received%2C%20and%20so%20I%20don't%20hold%20it%20against%20him.%20...%20He's%20been%20a%20great%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20has%20said%20that%20Trump%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20secure%20victory%20in%20the%20general%20election%20due%20to%20his%20strong%20legal%20obstacles%20and%20political%20opposition%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20he%20believes%20the%20timing%20of%20Trump's%20attack%20suggests%20the%20former%20president%20may%20feel%20threatened%20by%20his%20campaign%2C%20Ramaswamy%20refused%20to%20speculate%20on%20Trump's%20intentions%2C%20CNN%20reported.%20However%2C%20he%20reiterated%20his%20belief%20that%20his%20campaign%20is%20witnessing%20a%20%26quot%3Blate%20surge%26quot%3B%20in%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20speak%20for%20anybody%20else's%20attitude%20towards%20our%20campaign.%20What%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20is%20that%20you'd%20have%20to%20have%20your%20head%20stuck%20in%20that%20snow%20pile%20to%20believe%20that%20we're%20not%20having%20a%20late%20surge%20here%20in%20this%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20CNN%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy's%20remarks%20come%20after%20Donald%20Trump%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20party%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20calling%20his%20campaign%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful%26quot%3B%20and%20urging%20his%20supporters%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bwaste%26quot%3B%20their%20vote%20on%20him.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Indian-American%20leader%20is%20not%20'MAGA'%20(Make%20America%20Great%20Again)%20and%20a%20vote%20for%20him%20is%20a%20vote%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bother%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Trump%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BVivek%20started%20his%20campaign%20as%20a%20great%20supporter%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20President%20in%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20etc.%20Unfortunately%2C%20now%20all%20he%20does%20is%20disguise%20his%20support%20in%20the%20form%20of%20deceitful%20campaign%20tricks.%20Very%20sly%2C%20but%20a%20vote%20for%20Vivek%20is%20a%20vote%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bother%20side%26quot%3B%20--%20don't%20get%20duped%20by%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BVote%20for%20%26quot%3BTRUMP%2C%26quot%3B%20don't%20waste%20your%20vote!%20Vivek%20is%20not%20MAGA.%20The%20Biden%20Indictments%20against%20his%20Political%20Opponent%20will%20never%20be%20allowed%20in%20this%20Country%2C%20they%20are%20already%20beginning%20to%20fall!%20MAGA!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20marks%20a%20sharp%20reversal%20in%20the%20way%20Trump%20was%20speaking%20about%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20throughout%20the%20campaign.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20and%20most%20aggressive%20attack%20by%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Ramaswamy%2C%20which%20comes%20after%20a%20series%20of%20comments%20and%20posts%20Ramaswamy%20made%20that%20have%20angered%20Trump%20and%20his%20team%2C%20according%20to%20Trump's%20advisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Ramaswamy%20did%20not%20criticise%20Trump.%20Instead%2C%20he%20often%20praised%20him%20during%20the%20campaign%20trail.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20shared%20a%20picture%20on%20X%20that%20showed%20him%20posing%20with%20supporters%20donning%20%26quot%3BSave%20Trump%2C%20vote%20Vivek%26quot%3B%20T-shirts%2C%20which%20showed%20a%20picture%20of%20Trump's%20mug%20shot%20from%20when%20he%20was%20processed%20in%20Georgia%20at%20the%20Fulton%20County%20jail%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%2C%20which%20was%20shown%20to%20Trump%2C%20%26quot%3Binfuriated%26quot%3B%20him%2C%20CNN%20reported%20citing%20one%20advisor.%20The%20advisor%20noted%20that%20Donald%20Tr