%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67976042.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maldives%20Sets%20March%2015%20Deadline%20for%20Indian%20Troop%20Withdrawal%2C%20Says%20India%20to%20'Fast%20Track'%20Effort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17194015%2FF8cxCy0agAA1r64.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3EAfter%20setting%20a%20deadline%20of%20two%20months%2C%20Maldives%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20India%20has%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfast%20track%E2%80%9D%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20its%20military%20personnel%20stationed%20to%20operate%20aircraft%20primarily%20engaged%20in%20humanitarian%20missions%20within%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20archipelago%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deadline%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20Maldivian%20government%20as%20senior%20officials%20of%20both%20countries%20met%20in%20Mal%C3%A9%20on%20Sunday%20to%20discuss%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20being%20sworn%20in%2C%20the%20new%20President%20of%20Maldives%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20had%20formally%20requested%20India%20to%20remove%20its%20troops%20from%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20surprise%20as%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20election%20platform%20had%20revolved%20around%20the%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%20that%20targeted%20them%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20for%20his%20closeness%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fweeks-after-indian-troops-asked-to-leave-maldives-modi-holds-talks-with-mohamed-muizzu%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Dubai%20on%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP%20summit%20in%20November%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20had%20announced%20that%20a%20high-level%20group%20would%20discuss%20the%20contentious%20subject.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20the%20first%20meeting%20began%20in%20Male%2C%20with%20the%20Indian%20side%20represented%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20high%20commissioner%20Munu%20Mahawar%2C%20MEA%20joint%20secretary%20Puneet%20Aggarwal%20and%20senior%20defence%20ministry%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20officials%20at%20the%20table%20included%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20of%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Office%20Abdulla%20Fayaz%2C%20Ambassador%20at%20Large%20for%20foreign%20ministry%2C%20Ali%20Naseer%2C%20Maldives%20Ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Ibrahim%20Shaheeb%20and%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Force%20Abdul%20Raheem%20Abdul%20Latheef%2C%20as%20per%20local%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20public%20policy%20secretary%20at%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20Abdulla%20Nazim%20Ibrahim%20announced%20that%20President%20Muizzu%20has%20officially%20requested%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20by%20March%2015.%20This%20was%20made%20clear%20at%20the%20meeting%20underway%20at%20the%20Maldivian%20capital.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsmnews.mv%2Fen%2F131583%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Maldivian%20state%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20had%20received%20the%20latest%20information%20on%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives.%20Around%2088%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20are%20reportedly%20based%20in%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maldivian%20official%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20held%20%E2%80%9C12%20meetings%20on%20the%20issue%20so%20far%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20communique%20also%20added%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20to%20fast-track%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20readout%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20issued%20on%20Sunday%20evening%2C%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20deadline%20provided%20by%20Maldives.%20Neither%20did%20it%20mention%20that%20it%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%E2%80%9D%20to%20withdraw%20the%20military%20personnel%2C%20rather%20India%20claimed%20that%20the%20discussions%20were%20to%20continue%20operation%20of%20the%20Indian%20aircrafts%20in%20Maldives%2C%20which%20is%20operated%20by%20Indian%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37511%2FFirst_meeting_of_the_IndiaMaldives_High_Level_Core_Group%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MEA%20press%20note%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20stated%20that%20both%20sides%20%E2%80%9Cheld%20discussions%20on%20finding%20mutually%20workable%20solution%20to%20enable%20continued%20operation%20of%20Indian%20aviation%20platforms%20that%20provide%20humanitarian%20and%20medvac%20services%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20stated%20that%20both%20sides%20also%20held%20discussions%20on%20expediting%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20ongoing%20development%20cooperation%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20sides%20also%20held%20discussions%20on%20finding%20mutually%20workable%20solution%20to%20enable%20continued%20operation%20of%20Indian%20aviation%20platforms%20that%20provide%20humanitarian%20and%20medvac%20services%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Maldives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20agreed%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20the%20High%20Level%20Core%20Group%20in%20India%20on%20a%20mutually%20convenient%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Union%20external%20affairs%20minister%20broke%20silence%20over%20the%20India-Maldives%20row%20that%20was%20triggered%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep.%20%E2%80%9CPolitics%20is%20politics.%20I%20cannot%20guarantee%20that%20in%20every%20country%2C%20every%20day%2C%20everybody%20will%20support%20us%20or%20agree%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FdRoWp%23selection-1175.1-1175.342%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20seriously%2C%20as%20a%20solution%2C%20what%20we%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20do%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20success%2C%20is%20to%20build%20a%20very%20strong%20connect%2C%20so%20that%2C%20though%20the%20politics%20may%20go%20up%20and%20down%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20society%2C%20generally%20have%20good%20feelings%20towards%20India%20and%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20having%20good%20relations%20with%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.is%2FdRoWp%23selection-1175.1-1175.342%5C%22%3Eadded%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20returning%20from%20a%20state%20visit%20to%20China%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20President%20had%20indirectly%20criticised%20India%20by%20stating%20that%20the%20archipelago%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-muizzu-china-india-backyard-bully%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20in%20the%20backyard%20of%20any%20particular%20country%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20emphasised%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20procuring%20essential%20commodities%20from%20a%20single%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20now%2C%20all%20previous%20democratically%20elected%20heads%20of%20state%20of%20Maldives%20had%20chosen%20India%20as%20the%20first%20foreign%20port%20of%20call.%20But%2C%20Muizzu%20chose%20to%20break%20the%20pattern%20and%20went%20to%20Turkey.%20He%20also%20went%20to%20China%20for%20his%20first%20state%20v