likarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20including%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20presidents%20and%20Congress%20chief%20ministers%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20Revanth%20Reddy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20party%20had%20said%20that%20it%20had%20extended%20an%20invitation%20to%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%2C%20the%20only%20leader%20from%20Delhi%20was%20suspended%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20MP%20Danish%20Ali.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203%2C%202023%20in%20which%20over%20170%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%2C%20who%20started%20the%20yatra%20by%20first%20paying%20tributes%20at%20the%20Khongjom%20War%20Memorial%20in%20Thoubal%2C%20said%20that%20when%20the%20Congress%20party%20was%20deliberating%20upon%20where%20to%20begin%20the%20second%20instalment%20of%20the%20yatra%2C%20which%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-renames-rahul-gandhis-bharat-nyay-yatra-as-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erechristened%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20answer%20was%20clear%20to%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194535%2FVolunteer-stalls-outside-public-meeting-venue-in-Thoubal-Manipur-asking-people-to-join-the-yatra-by-giving-missed-calls.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194535%2FVolunteer-stalls-outside-public-meeting-venue-in-Thoubal-Manipur-asking-people-to-join-the-yatra-by-giving-missed-calls.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194535%2FVolunteer-stalls-outside-public-meeting-venue-in-Thoubal-Manipur-asking-people-to-join-the-yatra-by-giving-missed-calls-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVolunteer%20stalls%20outside%20public%20meeting%20venue%20in%20Thoubal%20Manipur%20asking%20people%20to%20join%20the%20yatra%20by%20giving%20missed%20calls.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20question%20came%20up%20about%20where%20to%20start%20this%20yatra%2C%20some%20suggested%20east%20some%20suggested%20west.%20But%20it%20was%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20can%20only%20start%20from%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20the%20continued%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20shows%20that%20the%20state%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-RSS%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Cideology%20of%20hate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20BJP-RSS%E2%80%99%20ideology%20of%20hate.%20Yes%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20what%20you%20valued%20but%20we%20will%20find%20it%20back.%20We%20understand%20the%20pain%20and%20hurt%20and%20loss%20sadness%20that%20people%20of%20Manipur%20have%20been%20through.%20We%20promise%20you%20and%20commit%20to%20you%20that%20we%20will%20bring%20what%20you%20value%2C%20the%20harmony%2C%20peace%20and%20affection%20that%20this%20state%20is%20known%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20north-south%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20was%20conducted%20from%20October%202022%20to%20January%202023%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20present%20leg%20will%20be%20an%20east%20to%20west%20yatra%20that%20will%20go%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20end%20in%20March.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20yatra%20was%20earlier%20expected%20to%20begin%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20capital%20Imphal%20but%20was%20moved%20to%20a%20private%20ground%20in%20Thoubal%20after%20the%20BJP%20state%20government%20refused%20to%20provide%20permission%20for%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20said%20that%20yatra%20will%20raise%20issues%20about%20economic%2C%20political%20and%20social%20inequalities%20as%20India%20is%20going%20through%20a%20period%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20less%20about%20us%20and%20more%20about%20you.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20our%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emann%20ki%20baat.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20want%20to%20listen%20to%20yours.%20And%20together%20with%20you%20the%20vision%20of%20India%20will%20not%20be%20of%20violence%20hatred%2C%20monopoly%20but%20of%20harmonious%20equitable%20and%20brotherhood%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20yatra%20will%20cover%206%2C700%20km%20and%20touch%20110%20districts%2C%20100%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20and%20337%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20what%20is%20the%20biggest%20mass%20outreach%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20media%20and%20communication%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20to%20reporters%20in%20Imphal%20that%20the%20yatra%20will%20be%20political%20but%20not%20electoral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20an%20electoral%20yatra%2C%20it%20is%20an%20ideological%20yatra.%20It%20is%20a%20political%20rally%20by%20a%20political%20party.%20There%20is%20a%20political%20purpose%20to%20protect%20the%20constitution.%20But%20not%20to%20discuss%20seats%20and%20impact%20on%20seats%20(for%20the%20elections)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERamesh%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20start%20from%20Manipur%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberate%20choice%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20yet%20to%20visit%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20bigger%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eanyay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(injustice)%20than%20this%20to%20Manipur.%20The%20tensions%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20months%20in%20which%20lakhs%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20many%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20yet%20he%20has%20not%20broken%20his%20silence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20has%20gone%20through%20agony%2C%20social%20harmony%20has%20been%20disturbed.%20This%20was%20going%20to%20be%20an%20east%20to%20west%20yatra.%20But%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20from%20Manipur%20to%20highlight%20what%20has%20been%20going%20on%20and%20to%20highlight%20that%20the%20PM%20has%20not%20met%20anyone%20from%20the%20state%20yet.%20We%20are%20hoping%20people%20of%20Manipur%20will%20see%20this%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20also%20took%20aim%20at%20Modi%20for%20not%20visiting%20Manipur%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20chanting%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20while%20carrying%20hatred.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(the%20PM)%20always%20comes%20here%20for%20votes.%20But%20when%20people%20of%20Manipur%20were%20suffering%20and%20facing%20violence%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20visit%20them%20even%20once%20while%20he%20had%20all%20the%20time%20to%20roam%20on%20the%20beaches%20and%20go%20snorkelling%20into%20the%20sea%20and%20sit%20and%20chant%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Ram%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMukh%20mein%20Ram%2C%20bagal%20mein%20choori%20mat%20karo%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20chant%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20and%20keep%20a%20knife%20on%20your%20side)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20peace%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocals%20who%20had%20come%20to%20the%20venue%20in%20Khongjom%2C%20Thoubal%2C%20said%20that%20he%20had%20come%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%20and%20harmony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThombi%2C%20an%20elderly%20woman%2C%20who%20had%20come%20from%20a%20village%20about%2020%20kms%20from%20Khongjom%20along%20with%20two%20other%20women%20from%20her%20village%20said%20that%20she%20had%20come%20to%20see%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20see%20peace%20and%20harmony%20and%20hear%20what%20he%20has%20to%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194620%2FThombi-left-corner-who-had-come-from-a-village-about-20kms-Khongjom-to-the-yatra.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194620%2FThombi-left-corner-who-had-come-from-a-village-about-20kms-Khongjom-to-the-yatra.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14194620%2FThombi-left-corner-who-had-come-from-a-village-about-20kms-Khongjom-to-the-yatra-300x225.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-692954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThombi%20(left%20corner)%20who%20had%20come%20from%20a%20village%20about%2020kms%20Khongjom%20to%20the%20yatra.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasguptaripla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20form