ard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftcpl-to-fund-2-acquisitions-with-cash-reserve-bridge-financing-md-d-souza-124011400225_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TCPL%2C%20which%20is%20a%20relatively%20new%20company%20in%20the%20FMCG%20sector%2C%20has%20made%20some%20acquisitions%20in%20the%20past%20to%20increase%20its%20play%20in%20the%20food%20segment%20and%20would%20continue%20to%20evaluate%20more%20options%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftcpl-to-fund-2-acquisitions-with-cash-reserve-bridge-financing-md-d-souza-124011400225_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftcpl-to-fund-2-acquisitions-with-cash-reserve-bridge-financing-md-d-souza-124011400225_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftcpl-to-fund-2-acquisitions-with-cash-reserve-bridge-financing-md-d-souza-124011400225_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Imran%20Khan's%20Party%20Must%20Drop%20Cricket%20Bat%20Symbol%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14150707%2FScreenshot-2024-01-14-at-3.06.50%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20on%20Saturday%20upheld%20a%20ruling%20stripping%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20party%20of%20its%20cricket%20bat%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Justice%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa%20announced%20the%20ruling%20on%20live%20television%2C%20saying%20the%20PTI%20had%20not%20held%20intraparty%20elections.%20Political%20parties%20in%20Pakistan%20must%20hold%20these%20elections%20in%20order%20to%20take%20part%20in%20the%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20first%20announced%20the%20ban%20on%20PTI%20for%20using%20the%20symbol%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%20The%20PTI%20then%20challenged%20that%20decision%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPTI%20on%20ruling%3A%20A%20%E2%80%98sad%20day%20for%20democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%2C%20by%20far%2C%20is%20the%20worst%20decision%20impacting%20millions%20of%20voters%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20ruling.%20PTI%20chairman%20Gohar%20Khan%20said%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20run%20as%20independents%20in%20the%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20spokesman%20Zulfi%20Bukhari%20decried%20the%20ruling%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csad%20day%20for%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20241%20million%20people%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20many%20areas%20facing%20high%20illiteracy%20rates.%20Without%20the%20cricket%20bat%20symbol%2C%20party%20officials%20have%20said%20some%20Pakistanis%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20recognize%20PTI%20candidates%20on%20the%20ballot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20candidates%20will%20now%20have%20to%20choose%20individual%20symbols%20instead%20of%20all%20running%20under%20the%20cricket%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kugelman%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20South%20Asia%20Institute%20at%20the%20Washington%20DC-based%20Wilson%20Center%20think%20tank%2C%20said%20the%20Pakistani%20government%20is%20cracking%20down%20on%20PTI%20ahead%20of%20general%20elections%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPTI%20leaders%20jailed.%20PTI%20electoral%20candidates%E2%80%99%20nomination%20papers%20denied.%20PTI%20online%2Frallies%20fundraisers%20blocked.%20Top%20PTI%20rival%E2%80%99s%20legal%20woes%20melt%20away.%20SC%20justices%20perceived%20as%20siding%20with%20PTI%20step%20down.%20PTI%20denied%20use%20of%20election%20symbol%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kugelman%20wrote%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20brazen%2C%20not%20subtle%2C%20pre-polls%20rigging.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20the%20military%20decide%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20next%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Pakistan%20is%20under%20a%20caretaker%20government%20ahead%20of%20the%20February%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20leader%20and%20former%20PM%20Imran%20Khan%20is%20currently%20behind%20bars%20and%20disqualified%20from%20running%20in%20next%20month%E2%80%99s%20vote.%20Seventy-one-year-old%20Khan%2C%20who%20served%20as%20PM%20from%202018%20to%202022%2C%20had%20a%20falling%20out%20with%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20formidable%20military%20and%20accused%20a%20former%20army%20chief%20of%20trying%20to%20kill%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENawaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20served%20as%20prime%20minister%20three%20times%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20upcoming%20vote%20after%20returning%20from%20exile.%20Sharif%20has%20been%20cleared%20of%20all%20legal%20charges%20against%20him%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20backed%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20report%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-imran-khans-party-must-drop-cricket-bat-symbol%2Fa-67974248%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705225698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F14150707%2FScreenshot-2024-01-14-at-3.06.50%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpakistan-imran-khans-party-must-drop-cricket-bat-symbol%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20symbol%20ties%20in%20with%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20image%20as%20a%20former%20cricket%20star.%20His%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%20believes%20a%20court%20ruling%20forcing%20them%20to%20lose%20the%20cricket%20bat%20will%20cost%20them%20during%20next%20month's%20vote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%